# Kalshi Makers & Takers Replication.
#
# Step Zero's own design goal (spec S3, "Step zero -- access check, hard
# gate") is that NOTHING below this line ever needs to be set. Kalshi's
# public market-data endpoints (/markets, /trades, /series, candlesticks)
# are documented as unauthenticated (security:[] in their OpenAPI spec,
# confirmed live 2026-07-15) and Step Zero verifies this empirically.
#
# DO NOT set the variables below unless `kmt step-zero` has explicitly
# printed a STOP / OPERATOR DECISION REQUIRED banner AND you have read
# reports/step_zero/findings.md AND you have made a deliberate decision to
# register for API access. This repository contains no code that registers
# an account on your behalf, by design -- see tests/test_scope.py.

# KALSHI_API_KEY_ID=
# KALSHI_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH=
